 </p>
 <p>
 <a id="fn7" name="fn7">7.</a> See, for example, Chauvet and Piger (2008), Hamilton (2011), and Berge (2015) for discussions of the real-time performance of several different classes of recession models. <a href="#f7">Return to text</a>
